These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, pineapple, potato, pear, carrot, apricot, pomegranate
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, ice-hockey, weightlifting, golf, lacrosse, basketball, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating pear##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
 5. the person eating cranberry is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
 6. the person eating cranberry is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
 7. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person eating pomegranate##8
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##7
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person eating apricot##1
11. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
13. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
14. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is skateboarding##7
15. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
16. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person eating carrot##8
17. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person eating cranberry##5
18. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
19. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
20. the person eating pear is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
21. the person eating cranberry is not to the right of the person eating cranberry##8
22. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Food           | apricot | potato | pomegranate | pineapple  | carrot  | pear | cranberry    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | skateboarding   | weightlifting   | golf | lacrosse | volleyball        | basketball |

