.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, tea, cola, hot-chocolate, coffee, lemonade
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, ritmeester, davidoff, tiparillo, cain, montecristo, bolivar
 1. the cain-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the montecristo-smoker is not the person drinking tea##6
 3. the davidoff-smoker is not to the left of the siglo-smoker##8
 4. the montecristo-smoker is between the siglo-smoker and the person drinking tea##2
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 8. the davidoff-smoker is not to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##8
 9. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##8
13. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
14. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
15. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
16. the person drinking tea is on the left of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
| Beverage   | lemonade | cola | tea    | 7up | hot-chocolate | milk | coffee |
| Cigar     | siglo     | montecristo   | ritmeester | cain | tiparillo       | davidoff        | bolivar      |

