.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, tram, taxi, skateboard, car, ship, van
7 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, turtle, bird, pony, snake, guinea-pig
 1. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 2. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
 3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 6. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 8. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 9. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
11. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
12. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the turtle##2
13. the owner of the bird is not the person driving the airplane##6
14. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
